dc_description_s: This data layer represents unincorporated places for Polk County, Wisconsin in 2021. [To identify the geographic location of Unincorporated Villages in Polk County, Wisconsin. Enhanced 911 and general mapping purposes.]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For access to the most current data available, please visit: https://www.co.polk.wi.us/landinfogisdataportal
